ets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁撐澳門狗咁一定好支持引渡去澳門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />按你邏輯香港特首林鄭同警察都係香港人,支持逃犯條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:44:31.000Z","msg":"你唔見二百萬人出來遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但你澳門狗有冇企過出來反政府啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ce0f39c702dfcafcfd4e9259fb6ffaa4f3976c0","tid":1242363,"uid":38358,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"岩啦，當日放棄香港人只顧自己<br />\n而家報應黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515e9eff831cd638f8e33c1cc7e28295aeb4e185","tid":1242363,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8884d7a0959821daab2f87fc058831d82e9ca31d","tid":1242363,"uid":105924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"23fb848d5ece32ef51d0d77d31c48df848a4af15","tid":1242363,"uid":141151,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:34:43.000Z","msg":"大劉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:49:19.000Z","msg":"一波未平一波又起，大劉今次你可以跪低幾多次"},{"pid":"0fe7287a68b61e8e7dd2f41db95a1211b767b353","tid":1242363,"uid":28202,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"723f7230f7223adc6460d271fae04bfdb49b1609","tid":1242363,"uid":127569,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"abd987b4a71ec9f035ea9c6ee41f070e41fe2a97","tid":1242363,"uid":28202,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3e0a83aa78c7e8ea1c87564fea82146eb6d47780","tid":1242363,"uid":127569,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:37:22.000Z","msg":"話我分化港澳果d死出來啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁撐澳門狗咁一定好支持引渡去澳門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />按你邏輯香港特首林鄭同警察都係香港人,支持逃犯條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:44:31.000Z","msg":"你唔見二百萬人出來遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但你澳門狗有冇企過出來反政府啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為人地暫時無林鄭咁仆街,唔駛200萬人,<br />\n連20人都唔駛,一早已經主動撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而到了 2015 年 12 月，澳門政府宣佈向立法會提交《區際刑事司法協助法》法案，只是該法案後來離奇地被政府「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>主動撤回」</strong></span>。澳門行政法務司司長陳海帆當時解釋，澳門一直與內地和香港商討刑事司法互助協議，惟三地法律體系差異相當大，特區政府須顧及區際間的協商安排，也要維持自身法律制度的完整性，協商工作有一定難度，所需時間亦較預期中長。由於協議尚未進入最後階段，故決定調整澳門內部立法工作的策略和進度。當局之後會再提交新法案，相信會更符合立法原則、更具操作性。"},{"pid":"1f69e769d39b7a4a2077954267ca8777c5bb39a8","tid":1242363,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:01:02.000Z","msg":"實捉到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06442b52e7a9ecad75e4a6c01022cb20d700e445","tid":1242363,"uid":211579,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:06:52.000Z","msg":"大劉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請多次御用律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi